name: Sprint Review Form
description: Review a sprint
title: "[😱 Scrum]: Sprint Review ✏️"
labels: ["scrum"]
body:
- type: input
  id: attendees
  attributes:
    label: Attendees
    description: Who's attending the sprint meeting?
    placeholder: "@..."
  validations:
    required: true
- type: markdown
  attributes:
    value: |
      Check delivered and remaining work together in Scrum board.
- type: textarea
  id: retrospective
  attributes:
    label: Sprint Retrospective
    description: As part of our commitment to inspect and adapt as a team we conduct a Sprint Retrospective at the end of every Sprint. Here are the results of our Sprint Retrospective.
    value: |
      **What went well?** ✏️
      
      **What didn't go so well?** ✏️
      
      **What improvements will be made for the next sprint?** ✏️
  validations:
    required: true
